data.description:
This 4-bedroom 31/2 bathroom estate home has been meticulously re-imagined with every detail taken into consideration to create a sophisticated modern masterpiece! Sleek fine finishes throughout, this home was taken down to the studs to update electrical & plumbing, expand kitchen, re-envision bathrooms, add smart technology features, replace flooring, and update storm protection by adding impact windows and doors.   The new dream chefs' kitchen showcases Calcatta quartz countertops, Viking appliances, expansive custom wood cabinetry, added prep sink, pass through window and accordion sliders leading to the lanai which is plumbed and ready for a new wet bar & summer kitchen creating the ultimate opportunity to enjoy year around indoor/outdoor living, dining and entertaining. Each bathroom is unique with impeccable accents such as granite flooring, marble walls, Riobel fixtures, floating sinks & toilets. The Primary Bathroom is highlighted by a 711 sq. ft. glass enclosed, 2 Kohler steam unit shower with a 24X24 Aqua Brass shower head and soaker tub boasting a luxurious spa experience. Steam heads and aromatherapy wells allow for the opportunity to add aromatic scents to enhance the steam experience. 
 
Additional accents and features include, newer 2019 roof, plantation shutters, new remote controlled ceiling fans, and all new 3" contemporary recessed lighting. Home is outfitted with the latest Smart Home Tech with new smoke detectors integrated into Google Nest and 3 Nest Thermostats. Three zone air conditioners with 2 replaced with 1.5-ton Trane split systems, the 3rd AC is an existing unit that had the motor replaced in 2023. Natural Gas fuels 2 tankless water heaters, the pool heater, the kitchen range and is ready to fuel the outdoor kitchen as well. 

The backyard with screen enclosed heated pool and lanai is a blank canvas awaiting the new buyer to complete and add to this picturesque 31,494 sq. ft. lot with breath taking vistas overlooking the recently renovated Lost City Golf Course. 

The home in the exclusive Estates section on a quaint cul-de-sac is within The City of Atlantis which is a non-mandatory fee country club lifestyle with 2 award-winning golf courses. The community is brightened by many annual events for its residents, such as the Spring Fling in April, an Independence Day firework display, a Halloween party, Christmas golf-cart parade, and a Christmas-tree burning party in early January. The city's Kintz park includes Tennis courts, basketball courts, a pavilion for events, and even a water park for children to enjoy. Self-contained with its own city hall, police department and in close proximity to Palm Beach International Airport, Atlantis is a paradise for full-time or seasonal residents.
